&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; We have offices in Boston, MA and New York, NY and would prefer interns/co-ops who can work from one of those locations—however, we will also consider remote candidates (US based only).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
